- 12. Temperature

Temperature (Â°C).

- 13. DewPoint

Temperature at which condensation starts.

Indicates moisture/humidity.

- 14. Pressure

Atmospheric pressure (hPa).

- 15. Humidity

Relative humidity (%) â€” moisture in air.

- 16. WindSpeed

Wind speed (m/s).

- 17â€“18. WindSine, WindCosine

Wind direction encoded cyclically.

Derived from wind angle.

- 19. WindAngle

Wind direction in degrees (0â€“360Â°).

-Â 20. CloudLevel

Cloud cover percentage (0â€“100).

- 21. WeatherType

